data.description: Take a look at this recently remodeled brick beauty with 3 levels of living. With a total of 5 beds and 3 baths, space will never been an issue. The large living room boast a real brick fire place, with hardwood floors throughout. The kitchen has been delicately crafted with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances. Modern meets historic in this home with the wooden staircase and the added luxury of a sun room for rest and relaxation. The large finished basement make the home ideal for related living. Seller to offer complete home warranty with purchase. Schedule your showing today!
